		<title>狗狗亂咬東西別急著罵！了解原因才能真正解決牠的「破壞行為」</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/21/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e4%ba%82%e5%92%ac%e6%9d%b1%e8%a5%bf%e5%88%a5%e6%80%a5%e8%91%97%e7%bd%b5%ef%bc%81%e4%ba%86%e8%a7%a3%e5%8e%9f%e5%9b%a0%e6%89%8d%e8%83%bd%e7%9c%9f%e6%ad%a3%e8%a7%a3%e6%b1%ba%e7%89%a0/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 21 Oct 2025 06:51:04 +0000</pubDate>
